| 24 | Having turned to L on LF, RF fwd without weight in front of Man at a 90° angle. R knee flexed (Small Press Line) | Facing against LOD | 1/4 to L between 23&amp;24 | B of LF with foot flat. Pressure on ball of RF | 8 |
| 25 | Replace weight fwd to RF, then turn on RF | Facing against LOD. End facing wall | 3/4 to R | BF | 1 |
